"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td>",
"        Angiography: vascular crowding with preserved distal vascular branching&bull;",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        Angiography: vague bullae, disrupted vasculature elsewhere in lung&bull;",
